<li id="cite_note-13"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-13">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Pamela Jones, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.groklaw.net/article.php?story=20091111151305785">An Explanation of Computation Theory for Lawyers</a>.</span></li>
